txt_content:
自定义了一个卖动物蛋蛋的NPC，可是，一直出现的都是默认的0号无用蛋。Damage参数无效，但是羊毛、金苹果、鱼的damage都可以。请问如何处理？
代码如下summon Villager ~ ~1 ~ 
{Profession:0,Career:3,CareerLevel:999,CustomName:"怕王建国的蛋蛋",Attributes:[{Name:generic.movementSpeed,Base:0.0}],
Offers:{Recipes:[
{maxUses:9999999,buy:{id:minecraft:emerald,Count:1},sell:{id:minecraft:spawn_egg,Damage:100,Count:1}},
{maxUses:9999999,buy:{id:minecraft:emerald,Count:1},sell:{id:minecraft:spawn_egg,Damage:95,Count:1}}
]}
}
复制代码

